---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Machine Learning — Jacob A. Torres"
  description="Machine learning projects by Jacob A. Torres."
>
  <h1>Machine Learning</h1>

  <p>
    I graduated in 2022 from Bloom Institute of Technology, where I studied
    full-stack web development, data engineering, and machine learning. I went
    on to become the lead web developer at Scheduler AI, an AI scheduling
    startup. Primarily I am a Python developer, with experience building web
    applications using Django and Flask, and ML applications using Python data
    science libraries. I'm also skilled in accessible UI development with HTML,
    CSS, and JavaScript/TypeScript.
  </p>

  <h2>Projects</h2>

  <ul class="project-list" aria-label="Programming projects">
    <li class="project-card">
      <span class="tag">Machine Learning</span>
      <h3>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/jacob-torres/Spotify-Song-Suggester"
          rel="external noopener"
          aria-label="Spotify Song Suggester on GitHub (opens in new tab)"
        >
          Spotify Song Suggester
        </a>
      </h3>
      <p>
        A machine learning application which uses a neural network to generate a
        Spotify playlist based on a single song.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="project-card">
      <span class="tag">Machine Learning</span>
      <h3>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/jacob-torres/AirBnB-Optimal-Price"
          rel="external noopener"
          aria-label="Airbnb Optimal Price on GitHub (opens in new tab)"
        >
          Airbnb Optimal Price
        </a>
      </h3>
      <p>
        A Flask web application which calculates the optimal price to rent an
        Airbnb property using machine learning.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
